               <history>
                  <provenance>The first part was copied for Besrāta Gabre'ēl (colophon, f.19a); The second part was copied for Empress Zawditu (1916-1930), who gave it to the Church of (our Lady of) Mount Qwesqwām (colophon, f. 188b). In Church (our Lady of mount)Qwesqwām when filmed.</provenance>
